1306
01:08:03,067 --> 01:08:04,533
Enough. That hurts.

1307
01:08:04,533 --> 01:08:05,633
Woman up!

1308
01:08:06,500 --> 01:08:08,333
It's not supposed to be easy.

1309
01:08:09,100 --> 01:08:10,367
It's revenge!

1310
01:08:10,367 --> 01:08:11,600
Isobel, it's okay now.

1311
01:08:11,600 --> 01:08:12,800
Enough.

1312
01:08:13,367 --> 01:08:16,633
Look, if Nyx wants to forgive,
then let her be.

1313
01:08:16,633 --> 01:08:18,167
That's her decision.

1314
01:08:18,167 --> 01:08:19,833
He hasn't even been
punished yet,

1315
01:08:19,833 --> 01:08:21,600
and you're already
forgiving him.

1316
01:08:21,600 --> 01:08:23,033
Nyx, let me remind you.

1317
01:08:23,467 --> 01:08:25,300
Ant is not only your own target.

1318
01:08:26,200 --> 01:08:28,300
He is our target!

1319
01:08:28,567 --> 01:08:30,167
I think everybody should agree

1320
01:08:30,167 --> 01:08:32,333
that this is quite unfair.

1321
01:08:32,333 --> 01:08:34,700
Hey, Isobel, calm down.

1322
01:08:34,700 --> 01:08:36,800
I'm all for this revenge thing,

1323
01:08:36,800 --> 01:08:40,200
but using his sexuality
against him is a bit much.

1324
01:08:40,200 --> 01:08:41,400
Right? Right?

1325
01:08:41,400 --> 01:08:42,867
You've got to be kidding me.

1326
01:08:42,867 --> 01:08:45,767
Ant said it himself, didn't he?

1327
01:08:45,767 --> 01:08:48,300
You all heard him, girls.

1328
01:08:48,300 --> 01:08:49,667
He's leaving campus.

1329
01:08:51,300 --> 01:08:53,300
That's enough revenge for me.

1330
01:08:53,733 --> 01:08:56,300
- That's my revenge. Please.
- Nyx!

1331
01:08:56,300 --> 01:08:58,533
He's just lying to you!

1332
01:08:58,567 --> 01:09:00,433
Isobel, that's enough.

1333
01:09:00,433 --> 01:09:01,667
That's enough.

1334
01:09:01,900 --> 01:09:05,333
Look, okay? Nyx said,
her target, her choice.

1335
01:09:06,167 --> 01:09:07,767
- Let it be.
- [APRIL] No, Marla.

1336
01:09:07,767 --> 01:09:09,800
Everybody needs to decide.

1337
01:09:09,800 --> 01:09:11,500
So what now, Nyx?

1338
01:09:11,500 --> 01:09:14,667
You told Ant we know
about the boys' GC.

1339
01:09:14,667 --> 01:09:16,500
That presents a systemic risk.

1340
01:09:16,500 --> 01:09:18,433
Ant's going to snitch on us
to the guys.

1341
01:09:18,433 --> 01:09:19,733
They'll realize

1342
01:09:19,733 --> 01:09:21,900
that we're the ones who took
their video in the shower room.

1343
01:09:21,900 --> 01:09:24,633
Cole will know that
I helped you.

1344
01:09:24,633 --> 01:09:25,900
I'll get in trouble.

1345
01:09:25,900 --> 01:09:28,733
Actually, no.
We'll all get in trouble.

1346
01:09:28,733 --> 01:09:31,367
You didn't even think of that?
That's just stupid.

1347
01:09:31,400 --> 01:09:33,667
Fine, I'm the fool.

1348
01:09:33,667 --> 01:09:36,167
I'm the stupid one then.
Fool, idiot, stupid.

1349
01:09:36,167 --> 01:09:38,333
You're all so smart and perfect!

1350
01:09:38,333 --> 01:09:41,233
Wow, sorry. That's all of you.
Genius! I love it!

1351
01:09:41,800 --> 01:09:44,767
- Nyx.
- Girls, girls, please.

1352
01:09:45,567 --> 01:09:48,333
We don't need to be insulting
each other, okay?

1353
01:09:48,800 --> 01:09:50,333
Wow.

1354
01:09:50,700 --> 01:09:54,267
When I decided to stimulate
the boys, you said a lot.

1355
01:09:54,800 --> 01:09:57,367
But Nyx gets a free pass,
because what?

1356
01:09:57,367 --> 01:10:00,333
Her decision is morally accepted
and mine isn't?

1357
01:10:00,333 --> 01:10:01,667
Are you a hypocrite?

1358
01:10:01,667 --> 01:10:03,433
Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!

1359
01:10:04,600 --> 01:10:06,567
Isobel, you're
crossing the line.

1360
01:10:06,567 --> 01:10:09,233
As Ken Blanchard once said,

1361
01:10:09,233 --> 01:10:12,267
"Most of us aren't as smart
as all of us."

1362
01:10:12,267 --> 01:10:15,200
So you know what?
Let's just vote. Let's vote!

1363
01:10:15,200 --> 01:10:18,400
I wasn't aware that there was
a voting process.

1364
01:10:18,400 --> 01:10:20,767
I thought we all wanted
the same thing.

1365
01:10:20,767 --> 01:10:23,433
Yeah, why are you acting like a
voting official all of a sudden?

1366
01:10:23,433 --> 01:10:24,600
Because you wanna vote, right?

1367
01:10:24,600 --> 01:10:27,533
You all wanna decide,
so let's take a freakin' vote!

1368
01:10:27,533 --> 01:10:28,800
Democracy!

1369
01:10:28,800 --> 01:10:32,700
So, raise your hands if you
wanna do this viciously, vile,

1370
01:10:32,700 --> 01:10:35,633
loathsome, evil, repulsive act

1371
01:10:35,633 --> 01:10:37,667
just to out Ant.

1372
01:10:37,700 --> 01:10:40,900
- Raise it.
- Who are the self-righteous,

1373
01:10:40,900 --> 01:10:44,733
rigid, feeling morally-superior,
and performative woke warriors

1374
01:10:44,733 --> 01:10:47,267
that want Ant to get away
with his whole crime scene

1375
01:10:47,267 --> 01:10:48,800
of leaking all
of our nude photos?!

1376
01:10:48,800 --> 01:10:50,233
Raise your cowardly hands!

1377
01:10:50,233 --> 01:10:51,667
- You're putting words--
- Me!

1378
01:10:54,000 --> 01:10:55,467
[SCOFFS]

1379
01:10:55,467 --> 01:10:56,800
Okay!

1380
01:10:56,800 --> 01:10:59,533
One, two, three.

1381
01:10:59,533 --> 01:11:00,767
One, two.

1382
01:11:01,867 --> 01:11:04,267
I'm sorry.
You've been outnumbered.

1383
01:11:04,267 --> 01:11:06,000
I demand a recount.

1384
01:11:06,000 --> 01:11:07,600
[DAPHNE] My god, recount?

1385
01:11:07,600 --> 01:11:09,800
- Oh, come on.
- [MARLA] Isobel.

1386
01:11:10,700 --> 01:11:12,933
What the hell
is the matter with you?

1387
01:11:12,967 --> 01:11:14,667
If we push through with this,

1388
01:11:14,667 --> 01:11:16,733
if we go on with this,

1389
01:11:16,733 --> 01:11:18,800
what does that say about us?

1390
01:11:20,467 --> 01:11:24,233
That we're not going
to let them step all over us.

1391
01:11:25,333 --> 01:11:28,567
But you're basically saying
we're just like them.

1392
01:11:30,267 --> 01:11:31,600
I can live with that.

1393
01:11:31,600 --> 01:11:34,700
Hey! Come on, girls!

1394
01:11:34,700 --> 01:11:36,333
Enough. Enough!

1395
01:11:36,333 --> 01:11:38,867
I mean, really?!

1396
01:11:38,867 --> 01:11:40,800
Is this really who we are now?

1397
01:11:40,800 --> 01:11:43,633
We're going to ruin
someone else's life?

1398
01:11:43,633 --> 01:11:47,700
But, Nyx, Ant ruined your life.
Are you okay with that?

1399
01:11:47,733 --> 01:11:49,700
Mind you, it's not just
your life he ruined.

1400
01:11:49,700 --> 01:11:51,500
- He ruined all five of ours.
- [DAPHNE] Wait!

1401
01:11:51,500 --> 01:11:53,800
We're all smart and pretty here,
aren't we?

1402
01:11:53,800 --> 01:11:57,667
I'm sure we can find
a better way to reach our goal.

1403
01:11:57,667 --> 01:11:59,967
- Dessalyn, shut your mouth!
- [DAPHNE] What, huh?!

1404
01:11:59,967 --> 01:12:01,400
You wanna spar?

1405
01:12:01,400 --> 01:12:02,833
[ISOBEL] All you talk about
is beauty and probabilities.

1406
01:12:02,833 --> 01:12:04,300
I swear...

1407
01:12:04,900 --> 01:12:07,700
revenge is not supposed
to be pretty!

1408
01:12:07,700 --> 01:12:09,933
The uglier, the better!
That's revenge!

1409
01:12:10,933 --> 01:12:12,367
Ugh!

1410
01:12:12,900 --> 01:12:13,800
There.

1411
01:12:14,700 --> 01:12:15,833
I deleted it.

1412
01:12:16,933 --> 01:12:18,700
We won the vote, right?

1413
01:12:18,733 --> 01:12:20,933
We all don't want to out Ant.

1414
01:12:20,933 --> 01:12:23,767
That's final. That's that.

1415
01:12:23,767 --> 01:12:27,967
Look, I know we all
agreed on revenge,

1416
01:12:27,967 --> 01:12:30,767
but we don't have to lose
ourselves in the process.

1417
01:12:31,767 --> 01:12:35,067
April, you told me
to trust my gut, right?

1418
01:12:35,067 --> 01:12:37,500
Well, this is me trusting it.

1419
01:12:37,500 --> 01:12:39,033
So, do you trust me?

1420
01:12:42,800 --> 01:12:43,933
April!

1421
01:12:43,933 --> 01:12:50,867
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

1422
01:12:54,967 --> 01:12:56,100
[ISOBEL GROANS LOUDLY]

1423
01:13:01,933 --> 01:13:04,367
You are all making
a big mistake!

1424
01:13:05,967 --> 01:13:07,900
And I thank you.

1425
01:13:22,567 --> 01:13:23,800
[PHONE CHIMES]

1426
01:13:23,800 --> 01:13:30,633
[STIRRING MUSIC CONTINUES]

1427
01:13:35,767 --> 01:13:42,600
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

1428
01:13:55,633 --> 01:14:00,700
[PAPER RUSTLING]

1429
01:14:11,133 --> 01:14:18,067
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

1430
01:14:38,167 --> 01:14:45,133
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

1431
01:15:08,867 --> 01:15:15,667
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

1432
01:15:35,700 --> 01:15:42,633
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

1433
01:16:06,567 --> 01:16:13,567
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

1434
01:16:38,000 --> 01:16:44,967
[TENSE MUSIC SWELLS]

1435
01:16:45,000 --> 01:16:46,100
[MUSIC STOPS]

1436
01:16:46,100 --> 01:16:53,067
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]
